印度傳媒則報道，中印兩軍已經由邊境另一衝突熱點班公湖完成撤軍，周六會舉行第十輪軍方談判，討論從基阿姆溫泉地區撤軍。<br />\n<br />\n印度曾聲稱去年邊境衝突有數十名解放軍死亡，印度就最少二十名士兵陣亡，但中方一直沒有證實有否死傷。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部指衝突發生後，中方為了維護兩國兩軍關係大局，推動局勢降溫緩和，保持高度克制，體現了中國作為負責任大國的氣度擔當。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人華春瑩重申，中方始終致力於通過對話妥善解決邊境爭端，希望同印方共同努力，維持邊境地區和平安寧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=424633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424633&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=abcba94d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424633&h=cd817f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=424633</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnOfav5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnOfav5.jpg&h=463fd540&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n4個?其他果D係多重影分身?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50731d40310cf712e3ca0c7955a4b3ad5609130","tid":2414383,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFhWEqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFhWEqr.png&h=ada03be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4個 你信？"},{"pid":"41663f4d5810747ada1ecbaf53cb14ab77c43f26","tid":2414383,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"咖喱國太可惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得4死，比d力呀屌~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0166dd645883605590e75835e3a1b0fd35baf95","tid":2414383,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci